{
  "stem": "2916.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they said, well, we want to give this business to the gentile store owners.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And very quickly they used the term Aryan.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Aryan store owners should make money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so they closed our store very quickly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there were other restrictions.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "A Jew law was passed which was stricter than the Jew law passed in Germany.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, in 1935, the Nuremberg law was passed which stripped the citizenship from the Jews of Germany and other restrictions.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The Hungarian Jew law was-- went much further.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It-- in 1938, it was passed, very shortly after occupation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were not permitted, for instance, to slaughter beef.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We could eat only chickens and geese.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They took away-- very quickly, everybody else's store was afterwards closed.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were not permitted to read newspapers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They took away our radios.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We shouldn't be able to hear the news from abroad.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because they said that the Hungarians-- that the Jews are enemy aliens.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That's how we were classified, and to make sure that you should not be able to listen to the news from England or the United States.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The allies were very, very-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] considered, you know, no, no.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And so we shouldn't be able to contact them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And, of course, shortly afterwards, the war broke out in 1939.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And we had to-- there was a blackout every night.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the-- the police would come especially to the Jewish homes to check if they are very carefully closing their shades.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Because they always said that the Jews probably will try to signal the allied planes with lights and all kinds of paranoid things they believed about the Jews.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And also, they conducted what they called raids on our homes.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
